---
title: Quick Spiced Pork Steaks & Beetroot Relish with Garlic Mash, Sautéed Cabbage & Baby Broccoli
description: What’s a quick and easy way to make succulent pork bursting with flavour? Add a tangy beetroot relish that’s
hard to beat, then team it with colourful veggies paired with garlic mash for a meal that’s all kinds of yum!

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
